REM Ducky Script - Harmless Pranks

REM 1. Rickroll Script - Opens a browser window to play a Rickroll video.
DELAY 500
GUI r                              REM Opens the Run dialog.
DELAY 500
STRING chrome https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ
ENTER

REM 2. Matrix Effect - Creates a Matrix-like effect by printing random numbers.
DELAY 1000                         REM Wait before starting the next prank.
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING cmd                         REM Opens Command Prompt.
ENTER
DELAY 500
STRING color 0a                    REM Sets green text on a black background.
ENTER
STRING :loop
ENTER
STRING echo %random%%random%%random%%random%%random%%random%%random%%random%
ENTER
STRING goto loop
ENTER

REM 3. Caps Lock Toggle - Repeatedly toggles Caps Lock on and off.
DELAY 1000
REPEAT 100
CAPSLOCK
DELAY 500
REPEAT 100

REM 4. Open Multiple Apps - Opens Notepad, Calculator, and Paint in quick succession.
DELAY 1000
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING notepad
ENTER
DELAY 500
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING calc
ENTER
DELAY 500
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING mspaint
ENTER

REM 5. Fake Error Message - Shows a harmless fake error message.
DELAY 1000
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING powershell
ENTER
DELAY 500
STRING [System.Windows.Forms.MessageBox]::Show('Your computer is infected!', 'Warning', 'OK', 'Error')
ENTER

REM 6. Flip the Screen - Temporarily flips the screen orientation, then returns it to normal.
DELAY 1000
CONTROL ALT DOWN                    REM Flips the screen upside down.
DELAY 5000                          REM Leaves it flipped for 5 seconds.
CONTROL ALT UP                      REM Returns the screen to normal.

REM 7. Make the Computer Talk - Uses PowerShell to make the computer say a message.
DELAY 1000
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING powershell -c (New-Object -ComObject SAPI.SPVoice).Speak('Hello, I am your computer')
ENTER
